***(ABSTRACT)
*
*        MEMBER $MDLENTH ON LIBRARYN.MVS CONTAINS THE MACRO '$MDLENTH',
*         WHICH CALCULATES THE SIZE OF THE CURRENT CSECT IN DECIMAL.
*
***(MODIFICATIONS UNIQUE TO BRUSSELS)
*
*        NONE
*
***(LOGIC SUMMARY)
*
*        N/A
*
***(INSTALLATION)
*
*        ADD THE MEMBER TO SYS2.MACLIB ( AS MEMBER '$MDLENTH' ).
*
***(TESTING)
*
*        N/A
